keys until you find them.

00:19:45.350 --> 00:19:47.510 align:middle line:84%
Emotional obesity
is the same thing.

00:19:47.510 --> 00:19:50.540 align:middle line:84%
I would rather you
spent all of your time

00:19:50.540 --> 00:19:53.150 align:middle line:84%
working on emotional obesity,
if you have the slightest

00:19:53.150 --> 00:19:55.160 align:middle line:84%
hint that you have it,
than anything else I'm

00:19:55.160 --> 00:19:56.952 align:middle line:84%
talking about, because
everything else will

00:19:56.952 --> 00:20:00.970 align:middle line:84%
fall into place once you
feel safer being thin.

00:20:00.970 --> 00:20:05.840 align:middle line:90%


00:20:05.840 --> 00:20:09.770 align:middle line:84%
And you know if you have
emotional obesity usually.

00:20:09.770 --> 00:20:11.510 align:middle line:84%
But there's always
kind of like a test.

00:20:11.510 --> 00:20:13.218 align:middle line:84%
Like, I remember one
time, the first time

00:20:13.218 --> 00:20:15.470 align:middle line:84%
I gave a big talk in Perth
was at the Burswood theater

00:20:15.470 --> 00:20:16.527 align:middle line:90%
and there was--

00:20:16.527 --> 00:20:17.360 align:middle line:90%
I was invited there.

00:20:17.360 --> 00:20:18.440 align:middle line:90%
It wasn't a seminar I was doing.

00:20:18.440 --> 00:20:20.660 align:middle line:84%
But there's hundreds of people,
maybe 500 or 600 people.

00:20:20.660 --> 00:20:21.910 align:middle line:90%
I'd never given a talk before.

00:20:21.910 --> 00:20:24.785 align:middle line:84%
And it was a really
exciting experience for me.

00:20:24.785 --> 00:20:26.285 align:middle line:84%
And afterwards, I
had this lady, she

00:20:26.285 --> 00:20:27.350 align:middle line:90%
was emailing me all the time.

00:20:27.350 --> 00:20:28.280 align:middle line:90%
Oh, you're a genius.

00:20:28.280 --> 00:20:29.510 align:middle line:90%
Nothing's ever worked for me.

00:20:29.510 --> 00:20:32.090 align:middle line:84%
Every-- my clothes are
just falling off me.

00:20:32.090 --> 00:20:34.550 align:middle line:84%
I have to buy new
clothes, blah, blah, blah.

00:20:34.550 --> 00:20:36.590 align:middle line:84%
And every week, she's
sending me an email.

00:20:36.590 --> 00:20:38.257 align:middle line:84%
And then one day, she
sends me an email.

00:20:38.257 --> 00:20:40.220 align:middle line:84%
She goes, oh, I had
a really bad week.

00:20:40.220 --> 00:20:43.670 align:middle line:84%
She said, I remember I was
walking down the street

00:20:43.670 --> 00:20:45.810 align:middle line:84%
and somebody said to
me, oh, you look great.

00:20:45.810 --> 00:20:48.910 align:middle line:90%


00:20:48.910 --> 00:20:50.080 align:middle line:90%
And I freaked out.

00:20:50.080 --> 00:20:51.480 align:middle line:90%
I couldn't handle that.

00:20:51.480 --> 00:20:52.500 align:middle line:90%
And I had a bad--

00:20:52.500 --> 00:20:53.190 align:middle line:90%
And she just said that.

00:20:53.190 --> 00:20:54.030 align:middle line:84%
I said, well, let's
talk, because I

00:20:54.030 --> 00:20:54.988 align:middle line:90%
knew what was going on.

00:20:54.988 --> 00:20:57.450 align:middle line:84%
And sure enough, when she
was a teenager, for example,

00:20:57.450 --> 00:21:00.900 align:middle line:84%
she had a date that
went out of control.

00:21:00.900 --> 00:21:03.420 align:middle line:84%
And that was a really
painful experience for her.

00:21:03.420 --> 00:21:06.237 align:middle line:84%
And ever since
then, she just feels

00:21:06.237 --> 00:21:07.820 align:middle line:84%
really uncomfortable
being attractive,

00:21:07.820 --> 00:21:10.180 align:middle line:84%
because she doesn't want
to repeat that experience.

00:21:10.180 --> 00:21:12.090 align:middle line:84%
Well, if that's the case, your
body's going to protect you.

00:21:12.090 --> 00:21:13.340 align:middle line:84%
So if you're losing the
weight, you're losing weight,

00:21:13.340 --> 00:21:14.760 align:middle line:84%
but you're not
addressing the fact

00:21:14.760 --> 00:21:18.520 align:middle line:84%
that your body wants
to be fat, you're

00:21:18.520 --> 00:21:21.070 align:middle line:84%
just driving with the
emergency brake on.

00:21:21.070 --> 00:21:23.622 align:middle line:84%
It's the whole
crux of the issue.

00:21:23.622 --> 00:21:26.080 align:middle line:84%
And I had another lady, the
first time I was on television,

00:21:26.080 --> 00:21:29.100 align:middle line:84%
she called me and she told me a
story she'd never told anyone.

00:21:29.100 --> 00:21:31.050 align:middle line:84%
And that was that when
she was 10 years old,

00:21:31.050 --> 00:21:34.050 align:middle line:84%
she was being abused
by a babysitter.

00:21:34.050 --> 00:21:37.260 align:middle line:84%
And it was actually
a female babysitter.

00:21:37.260 --> 00:21:40.450 align:middle line:84%
And the whole time
she was being abused--

00:21:40.450 --> 00:21:41.740 align:middle line:90%
this went on for three years--

00:21:41.740 --> 00:21:43.448 align:middle line:84%
she was gaining weight
and gaining weight

00:21:43.448 --> 00:21:44.830 align:middle line:90%
and gaining weight.

00:21:44.830 --> 00:21:46.840 align:middle line:84%
Eventually, she
gained so much weight

00:21:46.840 --> 00:21:49.390 align:middle line:84%
that the babysitter
stopped abusing her.

00:21:49.390 --> 00:21:51.930 align:middle line:84%
The babysitter goes, oh,
my god, you're so gross

00:21:51.930 --> 00:21:52.930 align:middle line:90%
and stopped abusing her.

00:21:52.930 --> 00:21:55.550 align:middle line:90%


00:21:55.550 --> 00:21:58.590 align:middle line:84%
But in that instance, fat
really did protect her.

00:21:58.590 --> 00:22:02.670 align:middle line:84%
Fat saved her life,
when no one else could.

00:22:02.670 --> 00:22:05.520 align:middle line:84%
And now 30 years down the road,
what do you think's happening?

00:22:05.520 --> 00:22:07.170 align:middle line:84%
Every time she loses
weight on a diet,

00:22:07.170 --> 00:22:09.510 align:middle line:84%
something happens, she freaks
out, she gains the weight.

00:22:09.510 --> 00:22:11.460 align:middle line:84%
What's freaking out is,
on a cellular level,

00:22:11.460 --> 00:22:13.290 align:middle line:84%
she doesn't feel
safe being thin.

00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:17.253 align:middle line:90%
That has to be addressed.

00:22:17.253 --> 00:22:19.670 align:middle line:84%
And I have kind of a quick way
now, when I talk to people,

00:22:19.670 --> 00:22:21.470 align:middle line:90%
I can zero in pretty quickly.

00:22:21.470 --> 00:22:22.970 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes I'll talk
to someone, I'll

00:22:22.970 --> 00:22:24.590 align:middle line:84%
say, OK, how much weight
do you want to lose?

00:22:24.590 --> 00:22:26.210 align:middle line:84%
I want to lose 40 kilos
and blah, blah, bah.

00:22:26.210 --> 00:22:28.490 align:middle line:84%
I go, OK, I want you to imagine
you're walking down the street

00:22:28.490 --> 00:22:29.750 align:middle line:84%
and you're in your
perfect ideal shape.

00:22:29.750 --> 00:22:31.850 align:middle line:84%
And everything's flowing in
your life, and it's beautiful,

00:22:31.850 --> 00:22:32.810 align:middle line:90%
and all this kind of stuff.

00:22:32.810 --> 00:22:33.610 align:middle line:90%
How do you feel?

00:22:33.610 --> 00:22:35.473 align:middle line:90%
I feel great.

00:22:35.473 --> 00:22:36.770 align:middle line:90%
Great.

00:22:36.770 --> 00:22:37.730 align:middle line:84%
So now you're walking
down the street.

00:22:37.730 --> 00:22:38.510 align:middle line:90%
And you know what?

00:22:38.510 --> 00:22:39.890 align:middle line:84%
You've got so much
energy coming out of you.

00:22:39.890 --> 00:22:41.473 align:middle line:84%
And you just look
so beautiful, you're

00:22:41.473 --> 00:22:44.270 align:middle line:84%
so attractive that people
can't help but notice you.

00:22:44.270 --> 00:22:45.070 align:middle line:90%
That's all.

00:22:45.070 --> 00:22:46.153 align:middle line:90%
They're just noticing you.

00:22:46.153 --> 00:22:48.610 align:middle line:84%
You're walking down the
street, they're turning.

00:22:48.610 --> 00:22:51.010 align:middle line:90%
They can't help but look at you.

00:22:51.010 --> 00:22:53.026 align:middle line:90%
How do you feel now?

00:22:53.026 --> 00:22:56.178 align:middle line:84%
A lot of times, people will say,
oh, I'm not feeling so good.

00:22:56.178 --> 00:22:58.220 align:middle line:84%
Or some people say, no,
I don't like that at all.

00:22:58.220 --> 00:22:59.710 align:middle line:90%
I don't want attention.

00:22:59.710 --> 00:23:01.960 align:middle line:84%
And then sometimes I imagine
I bring them up on stage,

00:23:01.960 --> 00:23:02.750 align:middle line:90%
oh, you don't get attention?

00:23:02.750 --> 00:23:03.330 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:23:03.330 --> 00:23:05.720 align:middle line:84%
So imagine you're up on stage
and there's thousands of people

00:23:05.720 --> 00:23:06.290 align:middle line:90%
there.

00:23:06.290 --> 00:23:08.248 align:middle line:84%
And there's a spotlight
on you and they're just

00:23:08.248 --> 00:23:09.800 align:middle line:90%
looking at you.

00:23:09.800 --> 00:23:10.753 align:middle line:90%
How do you feel now?

00:23:10.753 --> 00:23:12.170 align:middle line:84%
And I try to bring
it out of them.

00:23:12.170 --> 00:23:14.462 align:middle line:84%
And if there's the slightest
bit of uncomfortableness--

00:23:14.462 --> 00:23:15.770 align:middle line:90%
and you can try this--

00:23:15.770 --> 00:23:19.440 align:middle line:84%
if there's the slightest
bit of discomfort,

00:23:19.440 --> 00:23:21.090 align:middle line:84%
then you've got--
then your body,

00:23:21.090 --> 00:23:22.585 align:middle line:84%
it's not-- you're
not comfortable.

00:23:22.585 --> 00:23:24.210 align:middle line:84%
You're not comfortable
with the weight.

00:23:24.210 --> 00:23:26.752 align:middle line:84%
And you could be a male or
female for various reasons.

00:23:26.752 --> 00:23:28.710 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes, when I'm
working with you and I say,

00:23:28.710 --> 00:23:30.793 align:middle line:84%
well, just imagine these
beautiful white wings are

00:23:30.793 --> 00:23:33.760 align:middle line:84%
wrapped around you and that
people are looking at you,

00:23:33.760 --> 00:23:35.227 align:middle line:84%
but those wings
are shielding you.

00:23:35.227 --> 00:23:36.060 align:middle line:90%
How do you feel now?

00:23:36.060 --> 00:23:37.980 align:middle line:90%
And then instantly it changes.

00:23:37.980 --> 00:23:39.905 align:middle line:84%
And you've given
your body a message,

00:23:39.905 --> 00:23:42.030 align:middle line:84%
you've communicated to your
body that there's a way

00:23:42.030 --> 00:23:43.560 align:middle line:90%
to protect you without the fat.

00:23:43.560 --> 00:23:46.830 align:middle line:90%


00:23:46.830 --> 00:23:50.330 align:middle line:84%
Or a big column of light
that's protecting you.

