00:23:57.630 --> 00:24:00.250 align:middle line:84%
But just different tools,
visualization tools,

00:24:00.250 --> 00:24:01.870 align:middle line:84%
for communicating
that you're thin.

00:24:01.870 --> 00:24:05.020 align:middle line:84%
So you have to deal with these
two things in different ways.

00:24:05.020 --> 00:24:07.182 align:middle line:84%
But the chronic stress
has to be dealt with.

00:24:07.182 --> 00:24:09.140 align:middle line:84%
And the emotional obesity
has to be dealt with.

00:24:09.140 --> 00:24:12.940 align:middle line:90%


00:24:12.940 --> 00:24:15.010 align:middle line:84%
And there's different
ways to do it.

00:24:15.010 --> 00:24:17.210 align:middle line:84%
Then it's just a
question of application.

00:24:17.210 --> 00:24:19.690 align:middle line:84%
But for the chronic stress,
the best way to deal with it

00:24:19.690 --> 00:24:22.720 align:middle line:84%
is some sort of visualization
or meditation on a daily basis--

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:24.370 align:middle line:84%
before you go to
sleep at night, like

00:24:24.370 --> 00:24:25.810 align:middle line:84%
listening to the
visualization CD

00:24:25.810 --> 00:24:30.280 align:middle line:84%
