first thing in the morning.

00:24:30.280 --> 00:24:34.740 align:middle line:84%
Meditation inhibits the
signals in your brain

00:24:34.740 --> 00:24:36.610 align:middle line:84%
to a part of your brain
called the amygdala,

00:24:36.610 --> 00:24:39.740 align:middle line:84%
which is the seat of
fear and aggression.

00:24:39.740 --> 00:24:42.670 align:middle line:84%
And so it helps you
live a lower stress life

00:24:42.670 --> 00:24:44.170 align:middle line:84%
and does so many
other things, which

