there was cancer,

00:27:23.145 --> 00:27:25.270 align:middle line:90%
there was a car accident.

00:27:25.270 --> 00:27:28.500 align:middle line:90%
I started uni.

00:27:28.500 --> 00:27:30.600 align:middle line:90%
My grandfather died.

00:27:30.600 --> 00:27:34.780 align:middle line:84%
Whatever it was, if there's
a trigger to when your weight

00:27:34.780 --> 00:27:36.855 align:middle line:84%
started, that's not
a chemical trigger--

00:27:36.855 --> 00:27:39.230 align:middle line:84%
like I started taking medication
or something like that--

00:27:39.230 --> 00:27:41.710 align:middle line:84%
but if there's a trigger to
when your weight started,

00:27:41.710 --> 00:27:43.150 align:middle line:90%
then that's where you go.

00:27:43.150 --> 00:27:44.920 align:middle line:84%
You've got to deal
with that issue.

